    <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>It should be noted that RelyApply only requires an email and a set password created by user in order to submit reviews and/or companies that do not exist in the database. RelyApply will turn down requests to identify who wrote a review. Threatened parties should be aware that there have been a stream of documented cases where users <a href="http://itlaw.wikia.com/wiki/Anonymous_speech">right to be anonymous is upheld</a>. However, if the court does, in some way, find it necessary for you to be no longer anonymous for reasons including the involvement of investigative federal agencies, then RelyApply will have to disclose what information we required to create a profile.</p>
